Date: Sun, 12 Apr 2026 14:59:58 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] fix: resolve 12 broadcast pipeline bugs
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

🔴 Critical fixes:
- credits/adjust/route.ts: .update() → .upsert() (auto-create wallet on first credit)
- credits/adjust/route.ts: Add floor guard (prevent negative balance)
- lib/credits/service.ts: Auto-create wallet if missing in deductCreditsAtomic
- lib/credits/service.ts: Verify plan FK resolves to a real active plan (not just non-null UUID)
- api/contacts/route.ts: Add opt_in:true on manual contact create (broadcasts found 0 recipients)
- api/contacts/bulk-import/route.ts: Add opt_in:true on CSV import + upgrade to chunked upserts

🟠 Important fixes:
- whatsapp/webhook/route.ts: Verify token now actually checked (security fix)
- webhooks/whatsapp/route.ts: Add Content-Type header + catch inner errors (never return 500 to Meta)
- worker.ts: Unify langCode fallback to 'en' (was 'en_US', mismatched service default)
- api/contacts/route.ts: Non-tag segment filters no longer silently blast all contacts
- auth/google/callback/route.ts: Link default plan on Google OAuth new-user creation

🟡 Moderate fixes:
- seed-monster-plans.ts: Replace deleteMany+create with findFirst+update (preserve plan IDs across re-deploys)
- contacts/page.tsx: Show real total from API meta.total, not current page count (50)
